{"tid":2432533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一名男子報案稱疑收短訊偽冒銀行賬戶連結被騙13萬元","createTime":"2021-03-04T11:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T12:06:28.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1f685bcd3a963e970b5c3eab889509cf384b1a7","tid":2432533,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"警方昨日接獲一名29歲男子報案，指他收到銀行電話短訊，表示其戶口設定出現異常，需要點擊指定連結重新設定銀行賬戶。<span class=\"red\">他點擊連結後，按指示輸入戶口資料，其後收到戶口提款通知，指其戶口被提取共約13萬元</span>，懷疑受騙，於是報案。<br />\n<br />\n警方將案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，暫時未有人被捕，並提醒市民留意虛假銀行電話短訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577904-20210228.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577904-20210228.htm&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyvxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=6dc260a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577904-20210228.htm&h=5b669309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577904-20210228.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d62a65a5a9efd2d8f66983756922cf4f46c70988","tid":2432533,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgtXD4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgtXD4d.jpg&h=f900d400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇新聞，係釣魚網站嚟，喺個Domain name改少少，版面一樣，引你入去打密碼，之後就可以玩完，因為成個account俾人拎走，成個account啲錢就可以轉走晒，成副身家冇晒"},{"pid":"92e8c9e27cc01a6df9bacf56b71a26bd8a4c0595","tid":2432533,"uid":69125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:48:38.000Z","msg":"用中銀抵死"},{"pid":"8ee0d7e5612bab81e5d7eb0afdb63afd5025f0d1","tid":2432533,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"銀行應該會賠 13萬咁少. 廢事煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789bb59cbe41b056aca0038e3644b61a17d6cbf4","tid":2432533,"uid